org.datavec.api.transform.reduce.impl

Class GeographicMidpointReduction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.datavec.api.transform.reduce.impl.GeographicMidpointReduction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, ColumnOp, AggregableColumnReduction

    public class GeographicMidpointReduction
extends java.lang.Object
implements AggregableColumnReduction
    Given a set of latitude/longitude coordinates, encoded in Text writables with format "lat,long" (the delimiter is configurable), determine the geographic midpoint. See "geographic midpoint" at: http://www.geomidpoint.com/methods.html For implementation algorithm, see: http://www.geomidpoint.com/calculation.html
    See Also:
